     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p><b>Generated Narrative</b></p><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Resource \"ExampleRecommendationJustification\" </p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profile: <a href=\"StructureDefinition-recommendation-justification.html\">Recommendation Justification</a></p></div><p><b>ArtifactAssessment Version</b>: 0.1.0</p><p><b>ArtifactAssessment Publication Status</b>: active</p><p><b>date</b>: 2020-01-03</p><p><b>artifact</b>: <a href=\"PlanDefinition-ExampleRecommendationPlan.html\">PlanDefinition/ExampleRecommendationPlan</a> \"RecommendationPlan\"</p><blockquote><p><b>content</b></p><p><b>informationType</b>: rating</p><p><b>type</b>: Strength of recommendation <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"CodeSystem-ceosys-code-system.html\">CEOsys Code System</a>#strength)</span></p><p><b>classifier</b>: Strong for an intervention <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"CodeSystem-ceosys-cs-recommendation-strength.html\">Recommendation Strength</a>#strong-for)</span></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>content</b></p><p><b>informationType</b>: rating</p><p><b>type</b>: Overall certainty <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://build.fhir.org/codesystem-certainty-type.html\">EvidenceCertaintyType</a>#Overall)</span></p><p><b>classifier</b>: Very low quality <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://build.fhir.org/codesystem-certainty-rating.html\">EvidenceCertaintyRating</a>#very-low)</span></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>content</b></p><p><b>informationType</b>: rating</p><p><b>type</b>: Consensus <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"CodeSystem-ceosys-code-system.html\">CEOsys Code System</a>#consensus)</span></p><p><b>classifier</b>: Strong <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://build.fhir.org/codesystem-recommendation-strength.html\">StrengthOfRecommendationRating</a>#strong)</span></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>content</b></p><p><b>informationType</b>: container</p><p><b>type</b>: Certainty of evidence rating <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"CodeSystem-ceosys-code-system.html\">CEOsys Code System</a>#certainty-of-evidence-rating)</span></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>content</b></p><p><b>informationType</b>: container</p><p><b>type</b>: Net effect <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"CodeSystem-ceosys-code-system.html\">CEOsys Code System</a>#net-effect)</span></p></blockquote></div>"
